revision.text: '''Colbur''' is a type of [[Berries|Berry]] that can be planted in the [[Farm]]. It can be obtained by surrounding an empty plot with at least 1 [[Rabuta]], at least 1 [[Kasib]] and at least 1 [[Payapa]]. It has the unique effect of preventing the mutation of new Kasib berries.
revision.comment: Importing a new version from external source
